				<li id="16567059" class="cmnt-root" data="97" data-d="1648128816000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><a class="comment-username" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&u=130052" rel="nofollow"  target="_blank" style="color: #;">arhammahra</a></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t580097/Magic-Scorpion-Charm" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">24 Mar 2022 09:33</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16567059" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">You don&apos;t have to do anything related to Fingerslayer Blade and Ranni&apos;s quest to get the talisman.<br/>Here&apos;s what you need to do:<br/>1. Talk to Ranni to be in her service<br/>2. Talk to Seluvis<br/>3. Meet him at his tower and get the potion<br/>4. Beat Margit and enter Stormveil so Nepheli moves to Roundtable Hold<br/>5. Talk to Nepheli so she moves to the village<br/>6. Kill the village boss so she moves back to Roundtable<br/>7. Talk to Ofnir about Nepheli&apos;s despair and the option to give him the potion will unlock(not sure if you have to beat Godrick for him to talk to you)<br/>8. Give him the potion and return to Seluvis and he&apos;ll sell you his spells now(you don&apos;t have to buy them)<br/>9. Discover his puppets in the hidden area then talk to him about it and get one of the puppets<br/>10. Get starlight shards and rest 2 times to be able to buy another puppet<br/>11. Talk to him about his scheme and get the amber starlight, he&apos;ll give you the talisman once you give him the amber starlight.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16567059" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16567059" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">3</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>103</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>6</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16567059"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16567059" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16567059"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
